## What's New in v2.0

- **Soft neutral color scheme** — Warm off-whites, sage greens, muted stones instead of dark mode
- **Tasks** — Family to-do list with checkboxes and assignments
- **Meal planning** — Weekly dinner planner with quick editing
- **Emergency contacts** — Pediatrician, poison control, school, plumber
- **Computed ages** — Auto-calculated from DOBs (no more hardcoded "Age 5")
- **localStorage persistence** — Schedule, tasks, notes, meals survive page refresh
- **Netlify-ready** — Proper `netlify.toml` with `@netlify/plugin-nextjs`
- **Improved AI** — Better error handling, meal/task context in system prompt
- **Modern typography** — DM Serif Display + Outfit font pairing
